        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the<strong> chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[340ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> fish sauce </strong>and a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>– this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1722941902073-x200.jpg",
