            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the green beans are slightly tender, add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat – this is your <strong>Thai red curry</strong></p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-high and top the <strong>Thai red curry</strong> with your<strong> chopped cod</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for 5-6 min or until the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>Thai red cod curry</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
