        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Thai red cod curry</strong> over the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
